Name: UCSB
Description: A great university located along the California coast!

Name: Super Cucas
Description: A small, classic Mexican restaurant serving delicious authentic food; open late!

Name: Santa Barbara Airport
Description: A small hub primary public airport 7 miles west of downtown Santa Barbara.

Name: Costco Wholesale
Description: A massive warehouse selling bulk items like groceries, clothing, kitchen appliances, and much more. Also has a food court serving pizzas, chicken bakes, and churros.

Name: Nikka Ramen
Description: A quaint ramen shop serving traditional japanese noodle soup with a variety of toppings.

Name: Santa Catalina Residence Hall
Description: Student housing (primarily for first year students) located just off of UCSB campus. Prime location, close to Costco, Target, etc. Allegedly, parties are known to occur within the rooms of some students.
